title: Big Boi Interview and More

description:
Wednesday 6/21 – Today on the show we had Big Boi from OutKast join us this morning where he spoke about his new album, OutKast biopic and more. Also Charlamagne gave “Donkey of the Day” to Johnny Depp for being in debt and Angela helped some listeners out with “Ask Yee”.
